{"tid":2008970,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【搶攻議席】去年六月至今建制背景新工會多於泛民","createTime":"2020-05-09T11:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T11:53:07.000Z","uid":35763,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cc1a1a3b6ff757401ea691fadb0471239b5f8fb0","tid":2008970,"uid":35763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T11:53:07.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;<br />\n去年6月至5月2日，230個新工會成功登記，當中有洗錢報告主任、網絡紅人工作者等，新工會涵蓋各行各業。<br />\n本台調查過其地址及網頁，歸納當中51個是職工盟或泛民背景，56個則是由工聯會屬會或其他建制團體成立。<br />\n職工盟及工聯會都承認新成立的工會比往年多，對整體勢力分布的影響仍要待投票才知。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">未知的因素主要來自有123個背景不明的工會，當中多個工會用同一地址登記。</span><br />\n&rsquo;&rsquo;<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=390405&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D390405%26refer%3DShare&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d4oeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=a84361fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D390405%26refer%3DShare&h=c3395912\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=390405&amp;refer=Share</a>"}]}